airplane.description: A flying aircraft with wings and a smooth metallic body. Long fuselage with two wings and a tail section; smooth, aerodynamic body. It typically has white, silver, gray, smooth metal surface. Key features: two large wings, metallic smooth body, tail fin and engines, appears in sky or on tarmac, no visible legs or fur.

automobile.description: A four-wheeled vehicle on a road or parking area. Rectangular body with four wheels, windows, and headlights. It typically has varied solid colors, smooth metal and glass surfaces. Key features: four visible wheels, compact body, windows and headlights, road background, no animal parts or wings.

bird.description: A small feathered animal with wings and a pointed beak. Compact body with wings, beak, and tail; two small legs. It typically has feathers, brown, gray, or bright colors. Key features: visible wings and beak, feathery texture, often airborne, small size relative to background, no fur or limbs like mammals.

cat.description: A small furry animal with pointed ears and a long tail. Rounded head, pointed ears, four legs, long tail. It typically has fur in gray, brown, black, or white, soft texture. Key features: pointed ears, slim body and short snout, smooth short fur, long tail, smaller than dog or horse.

deer.description: A large brown animal with long legs and a slender body. Slender body with long legs, short tail, and sometimes antlers. It typically has brown, tan, smooth short fur. Key features: long legs, antlers (for males), slender body, forest background, larger than cat or dog.

dog.description: A four-legged furry pet animal with a rounded face. Four-legged body with rounded head, short snout, and tail. It typically has fur in brown, black, white, mixed patterns. Key features: rounded face and floppy ears, short fur or patches, domestic setting, medium size, visible paws.

frog.description: A small green amphibian with smooth skin and bulging eyes. Compact body with wide mouth, bulging eyes, and long hind legs. It typically has green or brown, moist smooth skin. Key features: green skin, bulging eyes, no fur, sits on leaves or near water, short body, long legs.

horse.description: A large animal with long legs, a mane, and a tail. Strong body with four long legs, mane, and long tail. It typically has brown, black, or white, smooth short fur. Key features: mane along neck, long legs, large body, smooth coat, visible hooves.

ship.description: A large vessel floating or moving across the water. Elongated hull, deck, and sometimes visible sails or superstructure. It typically has white, gray, blue, smooth metal or painted surface. Key features: large hull, water background, no wheels, horizontal body orientation, absence of wings.

truck.description: A large road vehicle with a cab and cargo section. Boxy front cab and long cargo area with multiple wheels. It typically has varied solid colors, metallic smooth surface. Key features: large cargo section, multiple large wheels, elevated height, rectangular cab, visible trailer in some cases.
